ezstruct is a tool for struct layout optimization. 

Purpose is to model, analyze and optimize the bitlayout of stucts.
Supports MS .pdb debugger info files.

== Install ==

I needed to run  "regsvr32 C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio 10.0\DIA SDK\bin\msdia100.dll" from an Administrator account to be able to add "msdia100.dll" as project assembly COM reference.